{"tid":1564732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣入］［續］我正式宣布新屋嶺義士關注度仲少過一首歌","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T06:00:47.000Z","uid":237528,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9c93fce2356c5dfa828b4444e4289b30f608ce7a","tid":1564732,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈新屋嶺義士關注度仲少過一首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n多謝手足們 終於有進步<br />\n今日係Twitter 見到好多人share番 新屋嶺義士既慘況<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過仲係無乜文宣圖同紀錄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國歌個d 已經進化到有Mv 同唔同版本<br />\n大家可唔可以出番多d力比番d資源係義士身上<br />\n義士永遠重要過國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家繼續同國際朋友宣掦［我地好慘被人迫害既訴息］<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新疆人權法快過香港過 係因為人地慘過我地<br />\n姐係咁 你平時見樂施會d宣傳刊物都描述非洲兒童好慘 影下兒童要執垃圾食 要香港人幫<br />\n以家人權法去到最後直路<br />\n加唔加到辣就睇大家既9.15表現同文宣既功力<br />\n我建議大家繼續舉美國旗 繼續唱美國國歌 <br />\nconnect 美國人<br />\n亦為9.17 gphone 同hocc 美國聽證會做勢 <br />\n大家亦可以係美國旗隊附近高舉班狗或狗官e.g.姐姐既大頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫上［制裁］兩個字 等美媒拍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁班國會議員張制裁名單就識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左新屋嶺集中營，仲有秘密警察，狗狗舉報熱線，特衰政府繼續擴大智能燈柱，蒙面法<br />\n愈講就覺得香港係納粹2.0/新彊2.0/文革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家出力煲 有幾大煲幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國歌同打狗D片就留番自己私底下圍爐取暖<br />\n國際戰線就share 番d 慘情野<br />\n<br />\n大家要知道 我地衰左<br />\n以上我所講會變真<br />\n可能又要唔知等幾多年見贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 打醒十二精神 未贏"},{"pid":"bc6104e91b0b4f92344531a902317cb068da7672","tid":1564732,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d497e03247de6b61b40fd4ac51ea8466d7e97aac","tid":1564732,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2285ea6c1d2ab56da4a04f47450994ab91faeeb5","tid":1564732,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"加辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><